[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man 'threatened to kill police officers' in north Wales

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has appeared in court charged with making threats to kill a number of police officers in north Wales.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Craig Michael Hughes is alleged to have made the threats during an online conversation with a confidential helpline based in the United States.
The 33-year-old, from Flint, appeared before Flintshire Magistrates' Court on Saturday.
No plea was entered and he was remanded in custody to appear before magistrates on Thursday.
